name: Wedding Event Map Design - 1 Sided
description:
Help your guests get around for your wedding, baby shower, corporate event or party.

Your map design includes 3 locations in the price. If you need more than 3 we can accommodate your request at $5 for each additional location. 

Will use directions you provide, your color scheme and other information.

Your map can be made into many sizes.

Please provide all details in the comments to seller section at checkout including your colors, dimensions, names and addresses of locations, preference of icons and any directions you may want used.

Need a 2 sided design?! We can do that too!


Map FAQs:
1.What is the turn around time? It ranges from 3 days to 2 weeks depending on the current work load and the complexity of the map. Good communication is key if you need your map in a hurry.

2. Can you do rush jobs? Yes at an additional cost, be sure to convo us to make sure we can accommodate your request. There is a rush fee that will be added to your order at the same time you purchase your map.

3. Can you print for me? Yes we can. Convo us for pricing information. be sure to let us know how many you would need and any paper requirements you may have.

4. What info do you need from me? We need the dimensions your map will be printed out, color scheme, addresses and names of locations, details like what type of map icons you might like, do you want a compass on it?

5. What fonts do you have? I have hundreds of different type styles. Not all look good on a map so please let me know several choices you have. Check out the website: www.dafont.com as I can use most of those.

By purchasing this listing, you are agreeing to my terms and policies which can be found here: http://www.etsy.com/shop/GoAgainstTheGrain/policy
